No

127
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,079
They're cheating

128
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,000
Cheating

129
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,160
Get lost

130
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,480
Don't let me see you again

131
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,040
You

132
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,199
Me

133
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,800
Hey

134
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,399
A guy about your age

135
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:19,000
with a seven or eight-year-old girl

136
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,600
came to your place looking for Ah Q

137
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,600
Keep an eye out for me

138
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,480
